4️⃣ OPTIONAL (ADMIN USERS) :-
-----------------------------

If you want admin + user roles later:

ALTER TABLE users ADD role VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'USER';

Example:

UPDATE users SET role='ADMIN' WHERE username='admin';
